**£4.92/m - [Order](https://quadhost.net/account/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=112&amp;utm_source=LowEndTalk&amp;utm_medium=offer-post&amp;utm_term=order&amp;utm_campaign=LET-OVZ-3G)**

###Network:

You can test our network using our [London](http://lg-ldn-uk.quadhost.net) &amp; [Varna](http://lg-var-bg.quadhost.net) LookingGlass instances. 

###Transparency:

We offer a [real time status page](https://quadhost.net/status/) showing current system load and resource utilisation on our website. We also have 3rd party independent monitoring recorded via [StatusCake](https://www.statuscake.com/).

###Company/Billing:

We are a registered as QuadHost Ltd. a limited company in England, UK. Registration no # 09661301. All prices exclude tax, EU residents will be charged tax.&lt;br /&gt;Pricing of £4.92 correct to meet $7/m rule as of 20:00 BST 16th June 2016 via Google UK.

###Want something else?

Need more disk, bandwidth, IP’s or cores?&lt;br /&gt;Not a problem, we have a range of virtual server solutions available, [open a sales enquiry](https://quadhost.net/account/submitticket.php?step=2&amp;deptid=4) and we will do our best to help!
